DESCRIPTION:<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><em><span style=\"color: #f1c40f; text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>BRADMAN MUSEUM </strong></span></em></span></p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif;\">The Bradman Museum celebrates the stories and people who shape the spirit of cricket. Enjoy our interactive exhibitions as the defining moments of the game come alive. </span></p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"> </p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif;\">At the heart of our Museum is the greatest cricketer of all time, Sir Donald Bradman. Bradman was renowned for the values of modesty, dignity, integrity and courage and these values resonate through the stories and people showcased in the Bradman Museum.</span></p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"> </p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif;\">We are proud of the way cricket brings together many cultures from around the world with the enduring power to inspire millions. </span></p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"> </p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif;\">Cricket was and always will be more than a game.</span></p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"> </p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif;\">AND THEN TO LUNCH AT </span></strong></p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"> </p> <p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; pointer-events: auto; font-size: 16px; color: #284937; margin-block: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><em><strong><span style=\"color: #f1c40f; text-decoration: underline;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: helvetica-w01-light, helvetica-w02-light, sans-serif;\">BURRAWONG VILLAGE HOTEL</span></span></strong></em></span></p> <p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1rem; line-height: var(--body-font-line-height); color: var(--image-block-collage-image-subtitle-color); font-family: adobe-garamond-pro; font-size: 19.504px; letter-spacing: 0.19504px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">Burrawang Village Hotel is the heart of the village of Burrawang – Southern Highlands.</p> <p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1rem; line-height: var(--body-font-line-height); color: var(--image-block-collage-image-subtitle-color); font-family: adobe-garamond-pro; font-size: 19.504px; letter-spacing: 0.19504px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">The hotel is a relaxed, welcoming and unique country pub for all to enjoy.</p> <p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; line-height: var(--body-font-line-height); color: var(--image-block-collage-image-subtitle-color); font-family: adobe-garamond-pro; font-size: 19.504px; letter-spacing: 0.19504px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">Offering a delicious menu for both lunch & dinner and extensive wine list and beers on tap.</p> <p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0px; line-height: var(--body-font-line-height); color: var(--image-block-collage-image-subtitle-color); font-family: adobe-garamond-pro; font-size: 19.504px; letter-spacing: 0.19504px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">Choose to dine by the open fire, quench your thirsty in the historic front bar or enjoy the vast beer garden with spectacular views across the Highlands.</p>
